ia's%20electronic%20warfare%20capability%20has%20evolved%20during%20the%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20disabling%20%26quot%3Bsophisticated%26quot%3B%20missiles%20provided%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20its%20Western%20allies%20by%20scrambling%20their%20GPS%20coordinates%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Clark%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20Hudson%20Institute%2C%20a%20US%20think%20tank%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66279650%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia's%20electronic%20warfare%20capability%20had%20significantly%20improved%20during%20the%20conflict%20with%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Russia%20was%20now%20deploying%20hundreds%20of%20small%2C%20mobile%20electronic%20warfare%20units%20along%20the%20front%20line%2C%20having%20previously%20relied%20on%20large%2C%20cumbersome%20units%20that%20could%20be%20easily%20targeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20Russian%20technologies%20were%20able%20to%20jam%20missile%20GPS%20coordinates%2C%20disable%20Ukrainian%20drones%2C%20and%20suppress%20Russian%20radar%20signals%20that%20were%20used%20by%20Ukraine%20to%20identify%20targets%20to%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20system%2C%20the%20R-330Zh%20Zhitel%2C%20is%20able%20to%20suppress%20satellite%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZhitel%20can%20jam%20a%20GPS%20signal%20within%2030km%20of%20the%20jammer%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Clark.%20%26quot%3BFor%20weapons%20like%20%5BUS-made%5D%20JDAM%20bombs%2C%20which%20use%20just%20a%20GPS%20receiver%20to%20guide%20it%20to%20the%20target%2C%20that's%20sufficient%20to%20lose%20its%20geolocation%20and%20go%20off%20target.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20JDAMs%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Fcommentary%2Fjamming-jdam-threat-us-munitions-russian-electronic-warfare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20UK%20think%20tank%20The%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20in%20January%20citing%20leaked%3C%2Fa%3E%20US%20documents%20in%20which%20officials%20expressed%20concern%20that%20Russia%20was%20jamming%20JDAM%20GPS%20coordinates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoint%20Direct%20Attack%20Munition%20(JDAM)%20bombs%20are%20among%20the%20weapons%20the%20US%20had%20provided%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20can%20be%20launched%20by%20air%20to%20hit%20targets%20up%20to%2045%20miles%20away.%C2%A0%20Like%20many%20long-range%20missiles%2C%20they%20rely%20on%20GPS%20coordinates%20to%20be%20guided%20to%20their%20target.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20a%20greater%20range%20than%20the%20HIMARs%20long-range%20missiles%20that%20Ukraine%20used%20to%20drive%20back%20Russian%20forces%20in%20a%20counteroffensive%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedefensepost.com%2F2023%2F03%2F08%2Fus-jdam-smart-bombs-ukraine%2F%3Futm_content%3Dcmp-true%26cn-reloaded%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Defense%20Post%20reported.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20also%20one%20of%20a%20number%20of%20weapons%20that%20Ukraine's%20Western%20allies%20hoped%20could%20help%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20new%20counteroffensive%20to%20drive%20back%20Russian%20invaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Russian%20defenses%20have%20proven%20resilient%20against%20Western-supplied%20weapons%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-tanks-ineffective-against-russian-minefields-ukrainian-general-2023-7%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Ewith%20Western%20tanks%20ineffective%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20huge%20minefields%20Russia%20has%20created%20to%20defend%20its%20positions%20in%20south%20and%20east%20Ukraine.%20Western%20offensive%20tactics%20have%