%20all%20walks%20of%20life.%20Their%20blessings%20got%20us%20this%20relief.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20them%20less%20than%2024%20hours%20to%20disqualify%20him.%20Now%20let's%20see%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20to%20reinstate%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20appeal%20against%20the%20conviction%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20maintained%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20are%20not%20in%20good%20taste%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20person%20in%20public%20life%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20petitioner%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20more%20careful%20in%20making%20speeches%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ramifications%20of%20disqualification%20not%20just%20affect%20the%20right%20of%20the%20individual%20but%20also%20the%20electorate%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20trial%20judge%20awarded%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20top%20court%20highlighted%20that%20it%20would%20not%20have%20attracted%20disqualification%20if%20the%20sentence%20was%20a%20day%20lesser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20in%20Karnataka's%20Kolar%20in%202019%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20a%20dig%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20come%20all%20the%20thieves%20have%20Modi%20as%20the%20common%20surname%3F%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20earlier%20challenged%20his%20conviction%20before%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Surat%2C%C2%A0where%20the%20appeal%20is%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691149140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fjicl2kus_rahul-gandhi_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-tweets-come-what-may-my-duty-remains-the-same-after-supreme-court-relief-in-modi-surname-case-4269023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20Defamation%20Case%3ASoon%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stayed%20the%20conviction%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20a%20criminal%20defamation%20case%20over%20his%20%26quot%3BModi%20surname%26quot%3B%20comments%2C%20the%20Congress%20scion%20said%20his%20duty%20remains%20the%20same.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-tweets-come-what-may-my-duty-remains-the-same-after-supreme-court-relief-in-modi-surname-case-4269023%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-tweets-come-what-may-my-duty-remains-the-same-after-supreme-court-relief-in-modi-surname-case-4269023%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-tweets-come-what-may-my-duty-remains-the-same-after-supreme-court-relief-in-modi-surname-case-4269023%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Allows%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Survey%20To%20Continue%20With%20Rider%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20survey%20by%20the%20country's%20top%20archaeology%20body%20should%20be%20done%20using%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-invasive%20method%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20has%20been%20given%20four%20weeks%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20a%20court%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Varanasi%2C%20which%20ordered%20the%20survey%20on%20July%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20had%20challenged%20the%20district%20court's%20survey%20order%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20request%20by%20the%20mosque%20committee%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20stop%20the%20district%20court's%20order%20directing%20the%20ASI%20to%20conduct%20the%20survey%20to%20determine%20if%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20on%20a%20pre-existing%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20finally%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20heard%20the%20matter%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masjid%20Committee%20said%20the%20ASI%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20will%20go%20into%20history%20and%20will%20%26quot%3Breopen%20wounds%20of%20the%20past%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20History%20has%20taught%20us%20something.%20What%20happened%20in%20December%201992%2C%20that%20raises%20suspicion%20and%20distrust%20at%20every%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20lawyer%20Huzefa%20Ahmadi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ASI%20survey%20intends%20to%20go%20into%20the%20history%20as%20to%20what%20happened%20500%20years%20ago.%20It%20would%20reopen%20wounds%20of%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ahmadi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20get%20into%20the%20past%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20the%20ASI%20to%20use%20a%20non-invasive%20method%20in%20its%20survey%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20ASI%20and%20the%20UP%20government%2C%20promised%20no%20excavation%20work%20will%20be%20done%20and%20no%20structure%20inside%20the%20mosque%20will%20be%20harmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20today%20resumed%20its%20scientific%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20compound.%20The%20survey%20began%20at%207%20am%3B%20it%20stopped%20for%20two%20hours%20between%2012%20pm%20and%202%20pm%20to%20allow%20for%20Friday%20prayers%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20security%20personnel%20has%20been%20deployed%20by%20the%20district%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20law%20and%20order%20near%20the%20Gyanvapi%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691149080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcm0r36u4_gyanvapi-