0studio%20to%20pay%20their%20last%20respects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnitin-desai-funeral-aamir-khan-ashutosh-gowariker-sonali-kulkarni-and-other-celebs-attend-last-rites-see-pics%2Farticleshow%2F102425302.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Australia%2C%20Pakistan...'%3A%20McGrath%20Picks%20%5C%22Best%20Four%5C%22%20Teams%20For%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20nearly%20two%20months%20left%20for%20the%20start%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20Australia%20pace%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Glenn%20McGrath%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F292-glenn-mcgrath-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGlenn%20McGrath%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20picked%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20four%26quot%3B%20teams%2C%20which%20are%20likey%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20semi-finals.%20McGrath%2C%20who%20is%20a%20three-time%20World%20Cup-winner%20and%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20feels%20that%20the%20upcoming%20showpiece%20event%20in%20India%20will%20be%20a%20nail-bitter.%20McGrath%20picked%20Australia%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20England%20and%20India%2C%20who%20are%20the%20hosts%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20as%20the%20four%20best%20teams%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20that%20I'm%20putting%20Australia%20in%20that%20four.%20Obviously%2C%20India%20is%20playing%20in%20their%20own%20conditions.%20England%20is%20playing%20some%20great%20cricket%2C%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20also%20playing%20fine.%20So%2C%20they%20are%20the%20best%20four%2C%26quot%3B%20McGrath%20told%20The%20Times%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20are%20the%20holders%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20while%20Australia%20(2015)%20and%20India%20(2011)%20haev%20won%20the%20tournament%20in%20the%20two%20editions%20prior%20to%20the%20last%20one%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20won%20their%20first%20and%20only%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20title%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20hosts%2C%20India%20are%20favourites%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20having%20won%20the%20tournament%20on%20home%20soil%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20two%20months%20to%20go%20for%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20things%20look%20far%20from%20settled%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20Question%20marks%20remain%20on%20the%20availability%20of%20some%20injured%20top%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20play%20their%20opening%20World%20Cup%20game%20against%20Australia%20in%20Chennai%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20moved%20to%20October%2014%20from%20October%2015%2C%20BCCI%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691146140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Firh4bd0o_glenn-mcgrath_625x300_27_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-pakistan-and-glenn-mcgrath-picks-best-four-teams-for-world-cup-4269083%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glenn%20McGrath%20is%20a%20three-time%20World%20Cup-winner%20and%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20tournament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-pakistan-and-glenn-mcgrath-picks-best-four-teams-for-world-cup-4269083%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-pakistan-and-glenn-mcgrath-picks-best-four-teams-for-world-cup-4269083%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-pakistan-and-glenn-mcgrath-picks-best-four-teams-for-world-cup-4269083%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ind%20vs%20Pak%3A%20How%20have%20arch-rivals%20fared%20after%20milestone%20T20Is%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691145776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102425255%2Cimgsize-49250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-west-indies%2Findia-vs-pakistan-how-have-the-arch-rivals-fared-after-milestone-t20is%2Farticleshow%2F102424779.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20have%20so%20far%20played%20223%20T20Is%2C%20winning%20134%20and%20losing%2080.%20They%20have%20had%203%20tied%20matches%2C%20of%20which%20they%20have%20won%201%20and%20lost%202%2C%20while%206%20have%20been%20no-results.%20Their%20overall%20win%20percentage%20stands%20at%20-%2060.08%25.%20In%20comparison%2C%20Team%20India%20who%20have%20played%20200%20T20I%20matches%20have%20so%20far%20won%20127%20and%20lost%2064%20games.%201%20match%20finished%20tied%2C%20while%20they%20have%20tied%20and%20won%203%20games.%20Their%20win%20percentage%20stands%20at%20-%2063.50%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-west-indies%2Findia-vs-pakistan-how-have-the-arch-rivals-fared-after-milestone-t20is%2Farticleshow%2F102424779.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TOI%20launches%20Mic%20On%20Hai%2C%20ft.%20Ankur%20Warikoo%20as%20the%20first%20guest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691145718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102425151%2Cimgsize-71798.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fthe-times-of-india-launches-mic-on-hai-ft-ankur-warikoo-as-the-first-guest-top-5-moments%2Farticleshow%2F102424856.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fthe-times-of-india-launches-mic-on-hai-ft-ankur-warikoo-as-the-first-guest-top-5-moments%2Farticleshow%2F102424856.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Varanasi%2C%20Occupants%20of%20Iconic%20Gandhian%20Institution%20Thrown%20Out%2C%20Land%20Taken%20Over%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04143320%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-04-at-11.42.32-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EUsurped%20is%20the%20appropriate%20word%20for%20what%20happened%20in%20Varanasi%20on%20July%2022%2C%202023%2C%20when%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20through%20the%20%C2%A0instrumentality%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20and%20the%20active%20support%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20state%20government%20authorities%2C%20including%20the%20police%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT_Va4gPcHKQ%5C%22%3Etook%20over%20the%20lands%20(and%20buildings%20existing%20thereupon)%3C%2Fa%3E%20legally%20belonging%20to%20a%20Gandhian%20institution%2C%20the%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh.%20All%20the%20occupants%20were%20evicted%20and%20eight%20persons%20who%20protested%20the%20action%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Fcampus-of-sarva-seva-sangh-vacated-8-detained%2Farticleshow%2F102049434.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewere%20detained%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20events%20of%20July%2022%20were%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20long-drawn%2C%20complicated%20saga%20going%20back%20to%20the%20time%20of%20independence%2C%20stretched%20over%20three%20distinct%20phases%20%E2%80%93%201948%20to%202006%2C%202007%20to%202022%2C%20and%20January%202023%20onwards.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20grasp%20the%20timeline%20for%20it%20points%20to%20a%20larger%20question%2C%20namely%20the%20place%20accorded%20to%20Gandhian%20institutions%20in%20the%20consciousness%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20journey%20post-independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhase%20I%3A%201948-2006%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EApril%201948%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20(ABSSS)%20was%20formed%20by%20Acharya%20Vinoba%20Bhave%20to%20propagate%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20and%20philosophy%20by%20merging%20five%20organisations%20engaged%20in%20constructive%20work%2C%20namely%20the%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Charkha%20Sangh%2C%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Gram%20Udyog%20Sangh%2C%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Gau%20Seva%20Sangh%2C%20Hindustani%20Taleemi%20Sangh%2C%20and%20Maharogi%20Seva%20Mandal.%20ABSSS%20was%20set%20up%20as%20a%20registered%20society.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMay%2015%2C%201960%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20ABSSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2Flink%2F1909026%5C%22%3Ebought%202.65%20acres%20of%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CPresident%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20through%20Divisional%20Engineer%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20Lucknow%E2%80%9D%20by%20way%20of%20a%20sale%20deed%20duly%20registered%20with%20the%20appropriate%20authority.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarch%201960%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20ABSSS%2C%20at%20the%20suggestion%20of%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20an%20institution%2C%20the%20Gandhian%20Institute%20of%20Studies%20(GIS)%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Gandhi%20Smarak%20Nidhi%20(Gandhi%20Memorial%20Fund)%2C%20at%20Rajghat%2C%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20where%20its%20own%20headquarters%20was%20located.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJanuary%2024%2C%201961%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Gandhian%20Institute%20of%20Studies%20(established%20under%20the%20auspices%20of%20ABSSS)%20was%20registered%20with%20the%20Registrar%20of%20Societies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJanuary%2026-27%2C%201961%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20Smarak%20Nidhi%20would%20set%20up%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20GIS.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMay%2019%2C%201961%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20ABSSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2Flink%2F4592649%5C%22%3Ebought%201.12%20acres%20of%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CPresident%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20through%20Divisional%20Engineer%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20Lucknow%E2%80%9D%20by%20way%20of%20a%20sale%20deed%20duly%20registered%20with%20the%20appropriate%20authority.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENovember%2028%2C%201963%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20lease%20deed%20was%20executed%2C%20leasing%20two%20parcels%20of%20land%20(1%2C453.78%20sq.%20yards%20and%20929%20sq.%20yards)%20totalling%202%2C382.78%20sq.%20yards%2C%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Gandhi%20Smarak%20Nidhi%20(the%20lessor)%20%E2%80%9Conly%20for%20the%20use%20of%20Gandhi%20Vidya%20Sansthan%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20the%20Institute%2C%20by%20the%20ABSSS%20(the%20lessee)%20for%20a%20period%20of%2030%20years%20at%20an%20annual%20rent%20of%20Re%201.%20The%20lease%20deed%20stated%20that%20if%20the%20lessor%2C%20GIS%2C%20shifted%20or%20ceased%20to%20function%2C%20the%20ownership%2Fpossession%20of%20the%20leased%20land%20would%20revert%20to%20the%20lessee%2C%20ABSSS.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMay%2020%2C%201970%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20ABSSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2Flink%2F5905563%5C%22%3Ebought%202.99%20acres%20of%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CPresident%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20through%20Divisional%20Engineer%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20Lucknow%E2%80%9D%20by%20way%20of%20a%20sale%20deed%20duly%20registered%20with%20the%20appropriate%20authority.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarly%201980s%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Social%20Science%20Research%20(ICSSR)%2C%20an%20organisation%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20support%20and%20fund%20research%20in%20the%20social%20sciences%2C%20contributed%20Rs%203%20lakh%20for%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20Institute%E2%80%99s%20library%20building.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E2002%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20assistant%20registrar%2C%20firms%2C%20societies%20and%20chits%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20moved%20Misc.%20Application%20No.%20243%20of%202002%2C%20before%20the%20additional%20district%20judge%2C%20under%20Section%2013(B)%20of%20the%20Societies%20Registration%20Act%2C%201860%2C%20seeking%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Institute%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20had%20ceased%20to%20function.%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20chairpersons%20of%20ABSSS%20and%20the%20UP%20Gandhi%20Smarak%20Nidhi%2C%20respectively%2C%20were%20ex-officio%20members%20of%20GIS%2C%20%C2%A0no%20notice%20was%20sent%20to%20them%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20necessary%20parties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2029%2C%202003%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Varanasi%20district%20magistrate%20Chandrabhanu%2C%20in%20Letter%20No.%201043(742)%20to%20the%20principal%20secretary%2C%20planning%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20(Lucknow)%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLand%20Ownership%20Status%3Cu%3E%3A%3C%2Fu%3E%20The%20land%20of%20Gandhi%20Vidya%20Sansthan%20%5BGIS%5D%2C%20Rajghat%2C%20Varanasi%20has%20been%20declared%20as%20belonging%20to%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20%5BABSSS%5D%20vide%20letter%20dated%2023.05.2003%20from%20Mr.%20Sandeep%20Pandey%2C%20Member%20Board%20of%20Management.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20Revenue%20Department%20got%20it%20examined.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAccording%20to%20this%2C%20Gandhi%20Vidya%20Sansthan%20is%20located%20in%20Khata%20No.%2033%2C%20A.No.%208%20M%20and%209%20M%2C%20of%20Village%20Qila%20Kohna%2C%20Pargana%20Dehat%2C%20Amanat%2C%20Tehsil%20Sadar%2C%20whose%20area%20is%202.134%20hectares.%20This%20land%20belongs%20to%20Jamman-14%20under%20Non-ZA.%20The%20name%20of%20Bhartiya%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20is%20inscribed%20as%20its%20owner.%20Photocopy%20of%20the%20report%20and%20site%20map%20received%20from%20the%20Deputy%20Collector%20(Sadar)%20is%20being%20attached%20for%20your%20perusal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04131756%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-04-at-11.24.52-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04131756%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-04-at-11.24.52-AM.jpeg%20810w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04131756%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-04-at-11.24.52-AM-300x169.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666629%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22456%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%2C%20Varanasi.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhase%20II%3A%202007-2022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMay%2028%2C%202007%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20additional%20district%20judge%20ordered%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20GIS%20and%20issued%20an%20additional%20direction%20to%20the%20secretary%20of%20higher%20education%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20constitute%20a%20management%20committee%20within%2045%20days%20so%20that%C2%A0%20studies%20did%20not%20get%20disturbed%20due%20to%20the%20dissolution.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E2007%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20ABSSS%20filed%20Writ%20Petition%20no.29975%20of%202007%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20seeking%20quashing%20of%20the%20additional%20district%20judge%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20May%2028%2C%202007.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhase%20III%3A%20January%202023%20onwards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJanuary%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Enter%20Moinuddin%2C%20a%20villager%20and%20resident%20of%20Kilakohna%20village%2C%20located%20in%20Dehat%20Amaanat%20pargana%20of%20Sadar%20tehsil%20in%20Varanasi%20district.%20Moinuddin%20submitted%20several%20applications%20to%20various%20authorities%2C%20including%20the%20deputy%20collector%20of%20the%20Varanasi%20circle%2C%20in%20Varanasi%20district%2C%20on%20January%2016%2C%202023%2C%20under%20the%20UP%20State%20Code%202006%2C%20stating%20that%20a%20particular%20piece%20of%20%C2%A0land%20had%20been%20%3Cem%3Ewrongly%3C%2Fem%3E%20entered%20in%20the%20records%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20when%20it%20actually%20belonged%20to%20the%20East%20Indian%20Railway.%20The%20application%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20Sadar%20tehsildar%20in%20Varanasi%20for%20an%20enquiry%20and%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJanuary%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20tehsildar%20wrote%20to%20the%20Northern%20Railway%20authorities%20enquiring%20about%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EApril%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Northern%20Railway%20responded%20to%20the%20tehsildar%20claiming%20ownership%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMay%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20delivered%20its%20judgment%20in%20Writ%20Petition%20no.29975%20of%202007%2C%20and%20decided%20that%3A%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E10.%20In%20the%20light%20of%20the%20above%20this%20court%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20dispute%20pertaining%20to%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20said%20property%20needs%20to%20be%20resolved.%20In%20case%20if%2C%20it%20is%20found%20that%20the%20petitioners%20are%20the%20true%20owners%20of%20the%20said%20property%20then%20possession%20of%20the%20said%20property%20should%20revert%20back%20to%20the%20petitioner.%20In%20this%20regard%20it%20is%20necessary%20that%20the%20competent%20authority%20should%20go%20through%20the%20various%20documents%20including%20the%20lease%20deed%20as%20stated%20by%20the%20petitioners%20which%20was%20executed%20between%20the%20petitioner%20no.2%20and%20respondent%20no.6.%20In%20case%2C%20it%20is%20found%20the%20petitioners%20are%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20property%20then%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20same%20should%20be%20reverted%20to%20the%20petitioners.%20To%20ascertain%20the%20aforesaid%20%3Cstrong%3Ethe%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20Varanasi%20is%20directed%20to%20examine%20the%20relevant%20records%20and%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion%20regarding%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20said%20property%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eexpeditiously%2C%20say%2C%20within%20a%20period%20of%20two%20months%20from%20the%20date%20a%20certified%20copy%20of%20this%20order%20is%20produced%20before%20him%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%2C%20and%20pass%20a%20reasoned%20and%20speaking%20order%20after%20examining%20all%20relevant%20documents%3C%2Fem%3E%20(emphasis%20added).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMay%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20With%20the%20understanding%20that%20a%20district%20magistrate%20(an%20executive%20officer%20appointed%20by%20the%20government)%20deciding%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edispute%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Epertaining%20to%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20said%20property%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20which%20the%20government%20itself%20was%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20to%20the%20dispute%2C%20was%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20conflict%20of%20interest%20and%20therefore%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%20ABSSS%20filed%20a%20civil%20suit%2C%20Case%20No.%20522%2F2023%2C%20at%20the%20%C2%A0court%20of%20civil%20judge%20(senior%20division)%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20seeking%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20a%20declaration%20of%20title%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6by%20way%20of%20decree%20declare%20that%20the%20plaintiffs%20are%20owners%20and%20in%20continuous%20possession%20of%20the%20property%20described%20below%20in%20Item%20%E2%80%98A%E2%80%99%20for%20decades%20and%20the%20plaintiff%20no.1%20is%20the%20sole%20owner%20and%20in%20possession%20of%20the%20same%20(emphasis%20added).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Following%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20in%20its%20judgement%20of%20May%2016%2C%202023%2C%20Varanasi%20district%20magistrate%2C%20S.%20Rajalingam%2C%20gave%20his%20decision%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20land%2Farea%20mentioned%20in%20the%20sale%20deeds%20dated%2015.05.1960%2C%2009.05.1961%20and%2020.05.1970%20belongs%20to%20Northern%20Railway.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Northern%20Railway%20administration%20issued%20the%20following%20notice%3A%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20informed%20to%20all%20the%20encroachers%20that%2C%20in%20the%20sequence%20of%20Letter%20No.%201339%20%2F%20Ra.Shah.First%2F2023%20of%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20%2F%20Varanasi%2C%20on%20June%2030%2C%202023%2C%20from%2009%3A00%20am%20on%20Friday%2C%20at%20the%20northern%20end%20of%20Kashi%20Railway%20Station%2C%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Northern%20Railway%20adjacent%20to%20GT%20Road%2C%20the%20demolition%20of%20illegal%20constructions%20constructed%20by%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20will%20be%20done%20by%20the%20Railway%20Administration.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETherefore%2C%20all%20the%20encroachers%20are%20informed%20to%20vacate%20the%20railway%20land%20immediately.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBy%20order%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ENorthern%20Railway%20Administration%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EDate%2027.06.2023%E2%80%B3%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20ABSSS%20filed%20Writ%20Petition%20no.%2021078%20of%202023%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20challenging%20the%20district%20magistrate%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20June%2026%2C%202023%2C%20and%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Northern%20Railway%20administration%20dated%20June%2027%2C%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuly%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20rejected%20the%20petition%20of%20ABSSS.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJuly%204%2C%202023%3A%20ABSSS%20filed%20a%20special%20leave%20petition%2C%20SLP%20no.14209%20of%202023%2C%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20(SCI)%2C%20challenging%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20judgment%20of%20July%203%2C%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuly%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20SCI%20declined%20to%20entertain%20the%20SLP%20saying%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20it%20is%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20observations%20made%20in%20this%20order%20is%20only%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20and%20the%20same%20should%20have%20no%20bearing%20on%20the%20merit%20of%20the%20contentions%20to%20be%20advanced%20in%20the%20Civil%20Suit%20(OS%20No.522%20of%202023)%20pending%20before%20the%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuly%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Railway%20administration%20forcibly%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%2C%20took%20over%20the%20land%20and%20buildings%2C%20evicting%20all%20occupants%20and%20throwing%20out%20all%20their%20belongings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20all%20this%20mean%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20the%20struggle%20of%20Gandhian%20institutions%20in%20the%20prevailing%20social%20and%20political%20context%20is%20much%20larger.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20major%20part%20of%20that%20struggle%20is%20presently%20in%20the%20legal%20arena%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20salient%20questions%20of%20legal%20issues%20and%20motives%20that%20the%20timeline%20raises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144113%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.30-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144113%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.30-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144113%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.30-PM-300x173.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144113%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.30-PM-1024x591.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666651%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22693%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20at%20the%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20major%20legal%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20first%20legal%20issue%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMentioned%20briefly%20above%2C%20it%20pertains%20to%20conflict%20of%20interest%20and%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%20occasioned%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20judgment%20of%20May%2016%2C%202023.%20The%20petition%20that%20the%20court%20was%20deciding%2C%20sought%20the%20quashing%20of%20the%20order%20of%20the%20additional%20district%20judge%20dissolving%20the%20Institute.%20In%20case%20the%20dissolution%20was%20not%20quashed%2C%20the%20petition%20sought%20an%20order%20for%20the%20disposal%20of%20GIS%E2%80%99s%20attests%20and%20properties%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20Memoranda%20of%20Association%20between%20itself%20and%20its%20founder%2C%20ABSSS.%20The%20high%20court%2C%20while%20recognising%20that%20this%20was%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20%3Cem%3Ea%20property%20ownership%20dispute%20between%20the%20government%20(Indian%20Railways)%20and%20a%20private%20party%2C%20ordered%20a%20government-appointed%20executive%20officer%2C%20district%20magistrate%2C%20to%20decide%20the%20entire%20issue.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20second%20legal%20issue%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20%C2%A0having%20effectively%20%3Cem%3Etaken%20away%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20court%20of%20the%20civil%20judge%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20to%20decide%20that%20title%20of%20the%20suit.%20It%20may%20be%20said%20in%20defence%20of%20both%20the%20constitutional%20courts%20that%20the%20high%20court%20has%20said%20in%20its%20judgment%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20it%20is%20always%20open%20to%20the%20petitioners%20to%20press%20the%20injunction%20application%20filed%20alongwith%20the%20aforesaid%20Original%20Suit%20before%20the%20Court%20below%20(and)%20The%20observations%20made%20by%20this%20Court%20would%20not%20affect%20the%20rights%2Ftitles%20of%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20on-going%20proceeding%20and%20the%20same%20would%20be%20decided%20on%20its%20own%20merits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Similarly%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20it%20is%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20observations%20made%20in%20this%20order%20is%20only%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20and%20the%20same%20should%20have%20no%20bearing%20on%20the%20merit%20of%20the%20contentions%20to%20be%20advanced%20in%20the%20Civil%20Suit%20(OS%20No.522%20of%202023)%20pending%20before%20the%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20meaning%20any%20disrespect%20to%20the%20two%20courts%2C%20it%20must%20be%20said%20that%20these%20pious%20and%20well-meaning%20observations%2C%20made%20on%20July%203%20and%20July%2017%2C%20have%20no%20practical%20relevance%20without%20staying%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Northern%20Railway%20threatening%20demolition%20starting%20%E2%80%9Con%20June%2030%2C%202023%2C%20from%2009%3A00%20am%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20building%20and%20the%20land%20was%20taken%20by%20force%20on%20July%2022%2C%202023.%20It%20is%20very%20much%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20possibility%20that%20the%20buildings%20may%20be%20demolished%20before%20any%20action%20is%20forthcoming%20from%20the%20lower%20civil%20court.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20invaluable%20books%20and%20documents%2C%20thrown%20about%20mindlessly%20by%20the%20police%20force%20during%20the%20eviction%2C%20have%20been%20irretrievably%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20third%20legal%20issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20pertains%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eonus%20of%20proof%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eregarding%20the%20correctness%2C%20validity%2C%20and%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20three%20sale%20deeds%3C%2Fem%3E.%20All%20the%20three%20sale%20deeds%2C%20as%20has%20been%20mentioned%20above%2C%20are%20between%20the%20%E2%80%9CPresident%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20through%20Divisional%20Engineer%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20Lucknow%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20are%20duly%20registered%20with%20the%20appropriate%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20magistrate%E2%80%99s%20decision%20of%20June%2026%2C%202023%2C%20makes%20for%20an%20interesting%20exercise.%20The%20first%20objection%20of%20the%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20as%20recorded%20in%20this%20order%2C%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20sale%20deed%2C%20only%20the%20designation%20of%20Divisional%20Engineer%20Northern%20Railway%20Lucknow%20is%20mentioned%2C%20his%20name%20is%20not%20mentioned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20plain%20wrong%20as%20the%20reverse%20side%20of%20page%202%20of%20the%20sale%20deed%2C%20dated%20May%2015%2C%201960%2C%20has%20a%20note%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20satisfied%20myself%20that%20this%20deed%20has%20been%20executed%20by%20Sri%20G.C.%20Banerji%2C%20Divisional%20Engineer%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20Lucknow%20in%20his%20official%20capacity.%20His%20attendance%20and%20signature%20are%20dispensed%20with%20and%20the%20doct.%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E)%20is%20admitted%20to%20registration.%E2%80%9D%20So%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20divisional%20engineer%20is%20not%20a%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20sale%20deed%20is%20also%20signed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CDivisional%20Superintendent%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20Lucknow%E2%80%9D%20along%20with%20his%20stamp%20on%20each%20page.%20The%20divisional%20superintendent%20(now%20re-designated%20as%20the%20divisional%20railway%20manager)%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20division%20in%20the%20railway%20system%2C%20a%20superior%20of%20the%20divisional%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20objections%20by%20the%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20as%20summarised%20in%20the%20district%20magistrate%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20June%2026%2C%202023%2C%20were%20as%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20Railways%20has%20never%20had%20any%20policy%20of%20selling%20land%20to%20any%20private%20organisation%20or%20person.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chief%20Engineer%20in%20Railway%20is%20authorised%20for%20licensing%20and%20lease%20deed.%20The%20Divisional%20Engineer%20does%20not%20have%20the%20said%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20non-vesting%20of%20right%20to%20sell%20in%20Divisional%20Engineer%20and%20non-presentation%20of%20authority%20letter%20regarding%20sale%20of%20railway%20land%20by%20Divisional%20Engineer%2C%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20said%20three%20sale%20deeds%20is%20questionable%2C%20the%20said%20sale%20deeds%20are%20forged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20astounding%20is%20that%20after%20listening%20to%20the%20above%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20asked%20ABSSS%20to%20provide%20proof%20that%20the%20divisional%20engineer%20did%20indeed%20have%20the%20requisite%20authority%2C%20%3Cem%3Eunder%20Railway%20Rules%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20to%20execute%20the%20sale%20deeds%2C%20recording%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20listening%20to%20the%20concerned%20parties%2C%20the%20petitioner%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20%5BABSSS%5D%20was%20asked%20to%20provide%20the%20records%20on%20the%20following%20two%20points%20for%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20case%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20Whether%20any%20correspondence%20%2F%20order%20has%20been%20issued%20by%20the%20Railways%20to%20sell%20the%20said%20gaate%20(sic)%20from%20the%20Railways%20or%20from%20the%20plaintiff%3F%20If%20done%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20same%20should%20be%20made%20available.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20Whether%20any%20letter%2Fnotification%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Railways%20to%20authorise%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20property%20mentioned%20in%20the%20sale%20deeds%20dated%2015.05.1960%2C%2009.05.1961%20and%20dated%2020.05.1970%20executed%20by%20Divisional%20Engineer%20Northern%20Railway%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astounding%20bit%20is%20that%20while%20Northern%20Railway%20is%20a%20party%20to%20the%20dispute%2C%20it%20is%20the%20other%20party%20to%20the%20dispute%20that%20was%20asked%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20actions%20that%20the%20Railway%20should%20have%20taken!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20on%20this%20basis%20of%20shifting%20the%20onus%20of%20proof%20that%20the%20following%20conclusion%20is%20recorded%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20of%20paragraph%20804%20Relinquishment%20of%20Railway%20Land%20of%20Railway%20Works%20Manual%20by%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%2C%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20release%20of%20the%20said%20land%20by%20the%20Railways%20and%20in%20the%20order%20of%20Point%20No.%201041%20Power%20of%20Sanction%20of%20Chapter%2010%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railway%20Code%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20no%20record%20related%20to%20any%20reference%20of%20Railway%20Board%20was%20made%20available%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%5Bobviously%20by%20the%20ABSSS%5D.%20The%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20and%20Section%2088%20of%20Registration%20Act%20provided%20by%20it%20are%20irrelevant%20in%20this%20case.%20Neither%20any%20letter%2Fnotification%20issued%20by%20the%20Railways%20to%20sell%20the%20property%20mentioned%3Cstrong%3E%20be%20made%20available%20by%20the%20representatives%20of%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20nor%20was%20any%20authority%20letter%2Fnotification%20issued%20by%20the%20Railways%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Divisional%20Engineer%20Northern%20Railway%20to%20execute%20the%20sale%20deed%3Cstrong%3E%20could%20be%20made%20available%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%5Bagain%2C%20obviously%20by%20the%20ABSSS%5D.%20%3Cstrong%3EThus%2C%20the%20petitioner%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Se%5Bv%5Da%20Sangh%20has%20completely%20failed%20to%20prove%20its%20ownership%20over%20the%20property%20allegedly%20purchased.%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20authentic%20evidence%2Frecords%20to%20confirm%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20sales%20letters%20of%20the%20years%201960%2C%201961%20and%201970.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%20clear%20from%20the%20above%20that%20the%20land%20mentioned%20in%20the%20sale%20deeds%20dated%2015.05.1980%2C%2009.05.1961%20and%20dated%2020.05.1970%20belongs%20to%20Northern%20Railway%20(emphasis%20added).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20issue%20of%20motive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20infer%20the%20motive%20behind%20this%20action%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20look%20at%20some%20documentary%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20chronology%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20lands%20were%20acquired%20through%20sale%20deeds%20and%20consideration%20paid%20into%20the%20government%20treasury%20(each%20of%20the%20three%20sale%20deeds%20specifically%20mention%20the%20treasury%20challan%20number%20and%20date)%20in%201960%2C%201961%20and%201970.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20were%20quiet%20for%20over%2030%20years.%20Then%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202002%2C%20the%20assistant%20registrar%20of%20societies%20initiated%20some%20action.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThat%20action%20lay%20dormant%20for%20five%20years%20when%2C%20in%202007%2C%20the%20additional%20district%20judge%20(ADJ)%20made%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EABSSS%20filed%20an%20appeal%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20against%20the%20additional%20district%20judge%E2%80%99s%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENothing%20significant%20happened%20to%20that%20appeal%20for%2013%20years.%20Then%2C%20a%20hitherto%20unknown%20individual%2C%20Moinuddin%2C%20entered%20the%20scene%20in%20early%20January%202023%20and%20a%20flurry%20of%20action%20followed%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20even%20the%20judiciary%2C%20which%20still%20continues.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20something%20happen%20in%20the%20months%20or%20years%20immediately%20preceding%20January%202023%20that%20caused%20this%20flurry%20of%20action%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144401%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.00-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144401%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.00-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144401%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.00-PM-300x145.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04144401%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-2.40.00-PM-1024x494.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22579%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20at%20the%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20now%3F%20The%20clue%20may%20lie%20in%20the%20documents%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2Flink%2F2100355%5C%22%3Eaffidavit%20filed%20by%20the%20Railways%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20July%2013%2C%202023%2C%20paragraphs%204%20to%2010%2C%20spread%20over%20five%20pages%20(pages%204-8)%20are%20titled%20Details%20of%20the%20Project%20in%20which%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20Alleged%2FClaimed%20Land%20Falls.%20These%20paragraphs%2C%20after%20describing%20the%20ancient%20and%20religious%20significance%20of%20Varanasi%2C%20give%20some%20details%20of%20what%20is%20%E2%80%9Cenvisaged%20%5Bas%5D%20a%20mega%20project%20of%20construction%20of%20%E2%80%98Inter-Modal%20Station%E2%80%99%20(IMS)%20at%20Varanasi%20(Kashi%20Railway%20Station)%20which%20contemplates%20creation%20of%20an%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E)%20novel%20infrastructure%20which%20could%20act%20as%20a%20gateway%20to%20road%20and%20waterway%20routes%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20rail%20network%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20affidavit%20mentions%20two%20sub-projects%20%E2%80%93%20upgradation%20of%20the%20Kashi%20railway%20station%20to%20provide%20%E2%80%9Cmodern%2C%20state%20of%20the%20art%20amenities%20for%20the%20passengers%20and%20the%20city%20dwellers%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20remodelling%20of%20Kashi%20yard%20(involving%20expansion%20of%20tracks%20and%20platforms%20to%20accommodate%20more%20trains%20and%20passengers%20with%20allied%20facilities%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20both%20for%20train%20operation%20and%20passenger%20comfort)%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20it%20does%20not%20disclose%20one%20vital%20piece%20of%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20online%20search%20unearthed%20two%20reports%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2Flink%2F1734234%5C%22%3Eone%20by%20the%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20and%20the%20National%20Highways%20Logistics%20Management%20Limited%20(NHLML)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20public%20sector%20companies%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2Flink%2F6237716%5C%22%3Eother%20by%20the%20international%20consultants%2C%20PwC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Slide%207%20of%20the%20NHAI%2FNHLML%20report%20shows%20the%20location%20of%20ABSSS%20land%20clearly%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20proposed%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlide%2010%20of%20the%20same%20report%20shows%20that%20three%20hotels%20(including%20one%20luxury%20hotel)%2C%20one%20Hotel%20Plaza%2C%20and%20a%20multi-storied%20commercial%20building%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%20Plan%20of%20IMS%20Kashi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EABSSS%20finds%20mention%20at%20two%20places%20in%20this%20report.%20Slide%2014%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSarva%20Se%5Bv%5Da%20Sangh%2C%20Mathh%20Shri%20Niwas%20BhagwanJi%20and%20Private%20Land%20would%20need%20to%20be%20acquired%E2%80%9D%20and%20Slide%2019%20says%20%E2%80%9CState%20Govt%2FVDA%20to%20acquire%20Sarv%5Ba%5D%20Se%5Bv%5Da%20Sangh%20land%20of%201.3%20acre%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20crucial%20giveaway%20in%20this%20report%20is%20its%20date%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJuly%2030%2C%202022.%20Herein%20lies%20the%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20as%20to%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20months%20or%20years%20immediately%20preceding%20January%202023%20that%20caused%20this%20flurry%20of%20action%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20not%20require%20rocket%20science%20to%20speculate%20that%20when%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cacquiring%E2%80%9D%20the%20land%20belonging%20to%20ABSSS%20came%20to%20be%20realised%20%E2%80%93%20on%2C%20or%20before%2C%20July%2030%2C%202022%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%E2%80%9Cauthorities%E2%80%9D%20came%20to%20an%20assessment%20that%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ethe%20Gandhians%20would%20not%20be%20willing%20to%20%E2%80%9Csell%E2%80%9D%20the%20land%20at%20any%20price%3B%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ethey%20would%20resist%20the%20process%20of%20acquisition%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flddashboard.legislative.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FA2013-30.pdf%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20land%20acquisition%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20force%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20would%20result%20in%20delay%20and%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%20the%20decision%20to%20%E2%80%9Cacquire%E2%80%9D%20the%20land%20by%20other%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20report%2C%20by%20consultants%20PwC%2C%20repeats%20many%20things%20contained%20in%20the%20NHAI%2FNHLML%20report%20but%20also%20reveals%20two%20new%20issues%20which%2C%20though%20not%20related%20to%20the%20ABSSS%20issue%2C%20are%20important%20from%20a%20larger%20societal%20viewpoint.%20Slide%2013%20of%20the%20PwC%20report%20states%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20site%20is%20approx.%20200m%20from%20the%20Kachhua%20wildlife%20Sanctuary.%20Wildlife%20clearance%20is%20required%20from%20National%20Board%20of%20Wildlife%20(NBWL)%20for%20development%20of%20project%20within%2010%20km%20of%20protected%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlide%2015%20of%20the%20report%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20site%20is%20abutting%20the%20Rajghat%20archaeological%20site%2C%20which%20is%20under%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI).%20Construction%20is%20prohibited%20within%20100m%20range%20from%20the%20boundary%20of%20the%20heritage%20site%2C%20and%20is%20known%20as%20prohibited%20area.%20This%20may%20lead%20to%20some%20non-usable%20area%20for%20IMS%20development%20in%20the%20available%20land.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20100%20m%20to%20300m%2C%20the%20area%20is%20known%20as%20regulated%20area.%20For%20construction%20in%20regulated%20area%2C%20approval%20from%20National%20Monuments%20Authority%20is%20required%20which%20takes%20approx.%203-4%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conclusion%20that%20logically%20flows%20from%20the%20above%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20There%20was%20an%20urgency%20to%20%E2%80%9Cacquire%E2%80%9D%20the%20land%20owned%20by%20the%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%20for%20the%20commercial%20development%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Inter-Modal%20Station%E2%80%99%20at%20Varanasi%20(Kashi%20Railway%20Station).%20As%20straightforward%20legal%20means%20were%20not%20likely%20to%20work%2C%20the%20purpose%20would%20have%20to%20be%20achieved%20by%20hook%20or%20by%20crook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20Gandhian%20struggle%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJagdeep%20S.%20Chhokar%20is%20a%20concerned%20citizen.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691145048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04143320%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-04-at-11.42.32-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-varanasi-occupants-of-iconic-gandhian-institution-thrown-out-their-land-taken-over%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fact%20that%20the%20land%20legally%20belonged%20to%20the%20Akhil%20Bharat%20Sarva%20Seva%20Sangh%2C%20founded%20by%20Vinoba%20Bhave%20in%201948%2C%20was%20just%20a%20minor%20irritant%20for%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-varanasi-occupants-of-iconic-gandhian-institution-thrown-out-their-land-taken-over%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20surname%20case%3A%20Truth%20always%20wins%2C%20Rahul%20says%20after%20SC%20relief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691144793000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102427584%2Cimgsize-1226431.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frahul-gandhi-arrives-at-aicc-hq-after-sc-stays