ncident%20in%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20soccer%20player%20named%20Jesus%20Alberto%20Lopez%20Ortiz%20was%20killed%20after%20being%20attacked%20by%20a%20crocodile%20in%20the%20river%2C%20according%20to%20Spanish%20outlet%20%3Cem%3EMarca%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20remains%20unclear%20whether%20he%20drowned%20or%20succumbed%20to%20the%20animal's%20pressure%20during%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%20The%20horrifying%20event%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Canas%20River%2C%20where%20Ortiz%20leaped%20from%20a%20closed%20fishing%20bridge%20despite%20the%20known%20presence%20of%20crocodiles%20in%20the%20water%2C%20while%20he%20was%20exercising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20were%20left%20horrified%20as%20they%20watched%20a%20chilling%20scene%20unfold%2C%20with%20footage%20capturing%20the%20large%20creature%20swimming%20through%20the%20river%20with%20Ortiz's%20body.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20approximately%20140%20miles%20from%20Costa%20Rica's%20capital%20city%20of%20San%20Jose%20near%20the%20town%20of%20Santa%20Cruz%2C%20in%20the%20province%20of%20Guanacaste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ortiz%20was%20a%20member%20of%20Deportivo%20Rio%20Canas%2C%20an%20amateur%20club%20team.%20He%20had%20even%20appeared%20for%20the%20team%20in%20the%20Costa%20Rican%20Ascenso%20League.%20The%20team%20confirmed%20Mr%20Ortiz's%20death%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3Dpfbid0xBP42U7iRaPjFb71v6vxq9YUgVEW747meeoFZjmxshyUeoiamR1Z3k3QZGTjsZS2l%26id%3D100076235453412%5C%22%3EFacebook%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20deep%20sorrow%20we%20make%20public%20the%20death%20of%20our%20player%20Jesus%20Lopez%20Ortiz%20(Chucho)%20may%20God%20rest%20his%20soul%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marca.com%2Fen%2Flifestyle%2Fworld-news%2F2023%2F08%2F03%2F64cb99a1ca4741b7278b456f.html%5C%22%3Eas%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EMarca%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26q