%20violence%20that%20followed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20procession%20in%20Nuh%20not%20only%20left%20a%20trail%20of%20destruction%20in%20rural%20Mewat%2C%20it%20also%20made%20its%20presence%20felt%20amongst%20the%20wealthy%20in%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20July%2031%2C%20mobs%20sporting%20saffron%20and%20wielding%20sticks%2C%20guns%20and%20other%20weapons%20set%20fire%20to%20a%20mosque%2C%20killed%20a%20cleric%2C%20and%20burned%20down%20several%20shops%20owned%20by%20Muslims%20in%20Gurugram.%20The%20arson%20continued%20into%20the%20next%20day%2C%20forcing%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20shut%20down%20schools%20and%20ask%20people%20in%20offices%20and%20MNCs%20to%20work%20from%20home%20for%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20target%20of%20this%20violence%20was%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20Gurugram%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20daily%20wagers%2C%20%3Cem%3Emistris%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20fruit%20sellers%20and%20small%20restaurant%20owners.%20The%20arson%20was%20ostensibly%20%E2%80%98retaliatory%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20for%20some%20twisted%20reason%2C%20%E2%80%98justified%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKallu%20Mia%2C%20an%20elderly%20Muslim%20who%20owned%20a%20mattress%20shop%20in%20Sector%2066%20till%20just%20a%20day%20before%2C%20is%20in%20a%20daze.%20Sitting%20under%20the%20shade%20of%20a%20small%20neighbouring%20shed%2C%20he%20is%20staring%20at%20the%20smouldering%20remains%20of%20his%20shop.%20On%20the%20afternoon%20of%20August%201%2C%20in%20plain%20view%20of%20dozens%20of%20high-rise%20apartments%20in%20the%20area%2C%20a%20mob%20of%20about%20ten%20people%20doused%20his%20shop%20with%20petrol%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20it.%20The%20mob%20also%20threatened%20Muslims%20living%20in%20tin%20sheds%20nearby%20that%20if%20they%20do%20not%20leave%20the%20city%2C%20they%20will%20face%20dire%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Fear%2C%20Depression%20in%20Indian%20Muslims%20Is%20Palpable%20Even%20Among%20Those%20Who%20Are%20%E2%80%98Privileged%E2%80%99%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ffear-depression-in-indian-muslims-is-palpable-even-among-those-who-are-privileged%5C%22%3EFear%2C%20Depression%20in%20Indian%20Muslims%20Is%20Palpable%20Even%20Among%20Those%20Who%20Are%20%E2%80%98Privileged%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Moradabad%2C%20the%20elderly%20Muslim%20shopkeeper%20came%20to%20Gurugram%20in%202021.%20I%20ask%20him%20the%20extent%20of%20his%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20lost%20at%20least%20Rs%203%20lakh%20worth%20of%20goods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20am%20talking%20to%20Kallu%20Mia%2C%20a%20local%20%3Cem%3Edoodhwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(milkman)%20stops%20his%20tempo%20next%20to%20the%20charred%20remains%2C%20strides%20up%20to%20us%2C%20interrupts%20our%20conversation%20and%20proclaims%20loudly%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20mob%20has%20no%20face!%20How%20do%20you%20know%20those%20who%20attacked%20his%20shop%20were%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20Hindus%3F%20How%20do%20you%20know%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20his%20enemies%3F%20Why%20are%20you%20media%20people%20spreading%20lies%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20guilty%20conscience%20needs%20no%20accuser%E2%80%99%20comes%20to%20mind.%20I%20tell%20the%20man%20to%20please%20wait%20while%20I%20finish%20talking%20to%20the%20man%20whose%20shop%20has%20burned%20down.%20He%20continues%20to%20butt%20in.%20I%20finally%20ask%20Kallu%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20have%20any%20personal%20enemies%20who%20could%20have%20done%20this%2C%20as%20he%20is%20saying%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBewildered%2C%20the%20old%20Muslim%20shakes%20his%20head.%20The%20people%20who%20know%20him%20also%20shake%20their%20heads.%20The%20milkman%20continues%20to%20loudly%20theorise%20about%20mysterious%20political%20parties%20and%20%E2%80%9Cconspirators%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20give%20the%20government%20a%20bad%20name.%20He%20is%20probably%20hoping%20I%20will%20interview%20him%20as%20well.%20I%20ignore%20him.%20After%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20possibly%20realising%20that%20I%20am%20not%20his%20ticket%20to%20instant%20fame%2C%20he%20gets%20in%20his%20tempo%20and%20drives%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20cross%20the%20road%20to%20where%20more%20small%20shops%20have%20been%20burnt.%20A%20small%20crowd%20is%20gathered%20around%20the%20charred%20remains.%20An%20TV%20crew%20from%20a%20channel%20that%20squarely%20falls%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98godi%20media%E2%80%99%20category%20is%20also%20present.%20A%20young%20reporter%20in%20a%20suit%20replete%20with%20silk%20handkerchief%20is%20walking%20around%2C%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20to%20talk%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bespectacled%20man%20comes%20up%20to%20me%20and%20starts%20chatting.%20His%20name%20is%20Gopal%20and%20he%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Egolgappa%3C%2Fem%3E%20seller%20from%20about%20half%20a%20kilometre%20away.%20While%20I%20am%20talking%20to%20him%2C%20the%20reporter%20interrupts%20our%20conversation%20and%20starts%20asking%20Gopal%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20request%20the%20reporter%20to%20wait%20till%20I%E2%80%99m%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20man%20loses%20his%20temper%20and%20starts%20shouting.%20I%20marvel%20at%20how%20similar%20his%20sense%20of%20entitlement%20and%20lack%20of%20basic%20courtesy%20is%20to%20that%20of%20the%20milkman%20I%20just%20encountered.%20This%20is%20what%20majoritarian%20arrogance%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20my%20taxi%20driver%2C%20a%20tall%20strapping%20Haryanvi%2C%20who%20has%20driven%20me%20to%20many%20protests%20and%20andolans%20over%20the%20years%2C%20hears%20the%20shouting%20and%20comes%20and%20stands%20next%20to%20me.%20The%20reporter%20decides%20to%20let%20me%20finish%20my%20conversation%20and%20storms%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram's%20Badshahpur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Badshahpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20very%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20continues%20Gopal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20always%20the%20poor%20man%20who%20ends%20up%20suffering.%20The%20people%20who%20ran%20these%20shops%20were%20Mohammedans.%20They%20have%20left.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clarifies%20that%20he%20is%20a%20Hindu.%20I%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20feels%20that%20Hindus%20are%2C%20indeed%2C%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHindu%20kisi%20bhi%20angle%20se%20khatre%20me%20nahi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20replies.%20(The%20Hindu%20is%20not%20in%20danger%20in%20any%20way.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20media%20keeps%20telling%20us%20that%20Hindus%20are%20in%20danger%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20know%20what%20the%20media%20in%20this%20country%20is%20like%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20retorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20who%20is%20in%20danger%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20thief%20is%20in%20danger.%20The%20person%20who%20has%20done%20something%20wrong%20is%20in%20danger.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopal%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20tell%20me%20the%20heartbreaking%20story%20of%20the%20death%20of%20his%20three%20children%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown.%20I%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20has%20gotten%20any%20help%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20has%20helped%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20he%20says%20with%20a%20note%20of%20finality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20on%20our%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushil%2C%20another%20resident%20of%20the%20same%20area%20who%20has%20a%20grocery%20store%20nearby%2C%20also%20condemns%20the%20violence%20and%20decries%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20political%20games%2C%20it%20is%20always%20the%20poor%20who%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20evening%2C%20journalist%20Ravish%20Kumar%20talks%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6ghxFHm3nUw%5C%22%3Eapathy%20and%20silence%20of%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20rich.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20former%20NDTV%20anchor%20asks%20why%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Millennium%20City%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20only%20protest%20when%20their%20roads%20get%20flooded%20in%20monsoon%2C%20remain%20silent%20when%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20population%20is%20targeted.%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20censure%20of%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20residents%20is%20scathing.%20He%20even%20goes%20on%20to%20sing%20a%20song%20in%20English%20on%20his%20show%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20English-speaking%20%E2%80%98Gurugrammarians%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20has%20made%20an%20important%20point%20on%20his%20show.%20Gurugram%20is%20home%20to%2035%2C000%20CEOs.%20If%20those%20CEOs%20were%20to%20get%20together%20and%20ask%20the%20government%20to%20stop%20encouraging%20the%20politics%20of%20hate%20and%20ensure%20communal%20peace%2C%20the%20effects%20would%20be%20dramatic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20drive%20away%2C%20my%20taxi%20driver%20quietly%20notes%20that%20all%20the%20coconut%20sellers%20in%20Gurugram%20have%20disappeared.%20They%20are%20all%20Muslim.%20He%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20Muslim%20family%20has%20lived%20in%20my%20building%20for%20years.%20They%20are%20very%20fine%20people.%20The%20lady%20was%20a%20teacher%20who%20was%20always%20ready%20to%20help%20my%20son%20with%20his%20homework.%20This%20morning%2C%20their%20door%20was%20padlocked%2C%20and%20their%20car%20was%20gone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20pause%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9