cal%20condition%2C%20which%20affects%20one%20or%20two%20persons%20out%20of%20every%20million.%20It%20is%20characterised%20by%20muscle%20rigidity%2C%20spasms%2C%20and%20stiffness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disorder%20causes%20unpredictable%20muscle%20spasms%2C%20which%20can%20be%20triggered%20by%20stress%2C%20noise%2C%20or%20unexpected%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20syndrome%20affects%20the%20central%20nervous%20system%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20controlling%20voluntary%20movements%20of%20the%20body.%20Although%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20disorder%20is%20not%20completely%20understood%2C%20research%20suggests%20that%20genetics%2C%20autoimmunity%2C%20and%20environmental%20factors%20may%20play%20a%20significant%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691140080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F83toigag_celine-dion_625x300_09_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fceline-dions-sister-shares-update-on-her-health-hope-is-important-4268607%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celine%20Dion%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20stiff%20person%20syndrome%20last%20year%20due%20to%20which%20she%20cancelled%20her%20world%20tour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fceline-dions-sister-shares-update-on-her-health-hope-is-important-4268607%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fceline-dions-sister-shares-update-on-her-health-hope-is-important-4268607%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fceline-dions-sister-shares-update-on-her-health-hope-is-important-4268607%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Internet%20responds%20to%20Sara's%20latest%20shoot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691139800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102421598%2Cimgsize-25598.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%