ess-66402202%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66402202.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66402202.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Had%20Summoned%20German%20Envoy%20This%20Week%20Over%20Ariha%20Shah%20Case%3A%20MEA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04082458%2FScreenshot-2023-08-04-at-8.24.33-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20summoned%20German%20Ambassador%20Philipp%20Ackermann%20and%20called%20for%20early%20repatriation%20of%20an%20Indian%20baby%20girl%20who%20has%20been%20under%20foster%20care%20in%20Berlin%20for%20more%20than%2020%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20seven-month-old%20Ariha%20Shah%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20Youth%20Welfare%20office%20in%20September%202021%2C%20after%20an%20injury%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20authorities%E2%80%99%20attention%20by%20a%20hospital.%20The%20German%20authorities%20had%20placed%20the%20child%20under%20foster%20care%2C%20alleging%20harassment%20by%20her%20Indian%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20Ackerman%20was%20summoned%20this%20week%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20regarding%20Ariha%20were%20unequivocally%20conveyed%20to%20him%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20accorded%20high%20priority%20to%20this%20case.%20We%20believe%20that%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20rights%20and%20her%20rights%20as%20an%20Indian%20are%20being%20infringed%20upon%20by%20her%20being%20placed%20under%20German%20foster%20care.%20The%20German%20ambassador%20to%20India%20was%20summoned%20earlier%20this%20week%20and%20our%20concerns%20were%20clearly%20conveyed%20to%20him.%20We%20have%20also%20asked%20for%20early%20return%20of%20the%20child%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20did%20not%20give%20any%20additional%20details%20on%20when%20the%20ambassador%20was%20summoned%20to%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20swift%20repatriation%2C%20based%20on%20her%20being%20in%20the%20same%20linguistic%2C%20religious%2C%20cultural%20and%20social%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20opposition%20women%20lawmakers%2C%20including%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rajani%20Patil%2C%20NCP%20leaders%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20Vandana%20Chavan%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20had%20met%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20over%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAriha%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Dhara%20Shah%20had%20been%20in%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20gather%20support%20among%20parliamentarians%20to%20push%20for%20the%20release%20of%20her%20daughter%20from%20foster%20care%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20cultural%20differences%2C%20they%20have%20taken%20a%20strict%20stand%20and%20we%20want%20to%20speak%20against%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fwomen-mps-meet-jaishankar-seek-intervention-for-release-of-child-from-foster-care-in-germany-531441%5C%22%3EBachchan%20told%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2013%2C%20a%20district%20court%20in%20Germany%20had%20denied%20custody%20to%20Dhara%20and%20Bhavesh%20Shah%20based%20on%20two%20injuries%20Ariha%20had%20suffered%20in%202021%20%E2%80%93%20one%20on%20her%20head%20and%20one%20in%20her%20genital%20area.%20Though%20a%20case%20of%20assault%20was%20filed%20against%20her%20parents%2C%20it%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20negligence%2C%20and%20finally%20dropped%20altogether.%