y%20to%20federal%20charges%20that%20he%20orchestrated%20a%20plot%20to%20try%20to%20overturn%20his%202020%20election%20loss%20in%20what%20US%20prosecutors%20call%20an%20unprecedented%20effort%20by%20the%20then-president%20to%20undermine%20the%20pillars%20of%20American%20democracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-pleads-not-guilty-to-charges-he-tried-to-overturn-election-loss%2Farticleshow%2F102403820.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-pleads-not-guilty-to-charges-he-tried-to-overturn-election-loss%2Famp_articleshow%2F102403820.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-pleads-not-guilty-to-charges-he-tried-to-overturn-election-loss%2Famp_articleshow%2F102403820.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22High%20Court%20Defends%20Andaman%20Daily%20Wage%20Workers%2C%20Suspends%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Fines%20LG%20for%20Contempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FCalcutta_High_Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20a%20double%20bench%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20has%20ordered%20the%20immediate%20suspension%20of%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Island%20chief%20Secretary%20Keshav%20Chandra%20Thursday.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20ordered%20lieutenant%20governor%20D.K.%20Joshi%20to%20deposit%20five%20lakh%20rupees%20from%20his%20personal%20funds%20with%20the%20registrar%20of%20the%20Port%20Blair%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20also%20ordered%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnext%20senior%20most%20officer%20in%20the%20administration%E2%80%9D%20take%20over%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdischarge%20the%20functions%20of%20the%20chief%20secretary%E2%80%9D.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20order%20is%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20and%20the%20department%20of%20personnel%20and%20training%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20pertains%20to%20paying%20enhanced%20wages%20to%20over%204800%20daily%20wage%20employees%20of%20the%20local%20PWD%20and%20other%20departments%20with%20retrospective%20effect%20from%20September%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20bench%20had%20upheld%20these%20demands%20in%20an%20order%20passed%20in%20December%202022.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20that%20the%20workers%20were%20entitled%20to%201%2F30th%20of%20the%20pay%20at%20the%20minimum%20of%20the%20relevant%20pay%20scale%20plus%20dearness%20allowance%20for%20work%20of%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20as%20specified%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20In%20its%20latest%20order%2C%20the%20court%20has%20ordered%20the%20administration%20to%20withdraw%20the%20preconditions%20they%20had%20laid%20before%20the%20employees%20before%20release%20of%20payment%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnicobartimes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FDocScanner-May-9-2023-11-11.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclause%20(g)%20of%20its%20May%209%2C%202023%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20applicant%20has%20to%20submit%20an%20Undertaking%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20enhanced%20wages%20to%20be%20granted%20by%20the%20department%20shall%20not%20bestow%20any%20right%20upon%20him%20for%20regularisation%20of%20service%20against%20any%20vacant%20post%20in%20future%20or%20any%20additional%20wages%20for%20any%20previous%20period%20before%20the%20date%20of%20issue%20of%20this%20Administration%E2%80%99s%20Order.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Andaman%20Sarvajanik%20Nirman%20Vibhag%20Mazdoor%20Sangh%20had%20taken%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20LG%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20next%20date%20of%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ehearing%20on%20August%2017%2C%20the%20chief%20secretary%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20be%20present%20in%20person%20and%20the%20LG%20in%20virtual%20mode%20%E2%80%9Cand%20shall%20show%20cause%20as%20to%20why%20they%20should%20not%20be%20committed%20to%20prison%20for%20having%20committed%20contempt%20of%20court%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20the%20court%20took%20umbrage%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20contemnors%2C%20in%20this%20case%20the%20LG%20and%20the%20chief%20secretary%2C%20had%20not%20filed%20any%20affidavit%20on%20why%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20had%20not%20been%20implemented.%20Instead%20of%20challenging%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20in%20a%20higher%20court%2C%20the%20administration%20challenged%20the%20high%20court%20itself%20in%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20by%20a%20junior%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20deponent%20of%20the%20affidavit%20had%20the%20audacity%20to%20challenge%20and%20reopen%20the%20issues%20decided%20before%20the%20single%20bench%20and%20confirmed%20by%20the%20division%20bench%2C%20without%20challenging%20the%20same%20before%20a%20higher%20forum%E2%80%A6%20This%20conduct%20is%20ex%20facie%20contumacious%20and%20has%20reduced%20the%20contempt%20jurisdiction%20of%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20this%20court%20under%20Article%20215%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20to%20a%20mockery%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20findings%20of%20this%20court%20as%20recorded%20on%20July%2027%2C%202023%20are%20clear%20and%20explicit.%20The%20undertaking%20required%20by%20the%20administration%20from%20the%20DRMs%20as%20a%20precondition%20for%20release%20of%20payment%20has%20not%20been%20withdrawn%20till%20date%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20was%20further%20incensed%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20while%20the%20%E2%80%9Cadministration%20has%20condescended%20to%20withdrawing%20the%20requirement%20of%20signing%20the%20undertaking%E2%80%9D%20after%20government%20counsel%20spoke%20to%20them%2C%20it%20has%20not%20said%20anything%20about%20framing%20of%20any%20scheme%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20employees%20called%20daily%20rated%20mazdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20clearly%20finds%20flagrant%20and%20reprehensible%20contempt%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20contemnors%20Admiral%20D.K.%20Joshi%2C%20lieutenant%20governor%2C%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20and%20Shri%20Keshav%20Chandra%2C%20chief%20secretary%2C%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20administration%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said%20before%20suspending%20the%20chief%20secretary%20and%20penalising%20the%20LG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20are%20a%20Union%20territory%20directly%20administered%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691093091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FCalcutta_High_Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fhigh-court-defends-andaman-daily-wage-workers-suspends-chief-secretary-fines-lg-for-contempt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20Territory%2C%20which%20is%20controlled%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%20had%20sought%20to%20undermine%20implementation%20of%20a%20court%20order%20favouring%20'daily%20rated%20mazdoors'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fhigh-court-defends-andaman-daily-wage-workers-suspends-chief-secretary-fines-lg-for-contempt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Southern%20Airways%20Express%20Is%20Suing%20Former%20Pilots%20For%20Training%20Costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Florida-based%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20enforce%20a%20controversial%20employment%20clause%20that%20has%20gained%20national%20attention%20recently.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691090145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F64cbe7cf2000005e00f83977.