.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20toys%20that%20Kirat%20makes%20have%20a%20tribal%20folklore%20and%20story%20attached%20to%20them%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Zankla%20Studio%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20toys%20that%20represented%20people%20like%20me%20and%20others%20from%20my%20community.%20The%20markets%20are%20flooded%20with%20Spiderman%2C%20Mickey%20Mouse%20and%20Barbie%20dolls.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20to%20spread%20awareness%20among%20people%20about%20the%20existence%20of%20Northeastern%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20toy%20created%20at%20Zankla%20Studio%20carries%20a%20narrative%20native%20to%20the%20tribe%20or%20is%20a%20representation%20of%20a%20prominent%20person%20from%20the%20tribe%2C%20such%20as%20Ada%20Lowdoom%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Bodo%20traveller%2C%20Bodo%20Jwhwlao%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20Bodo%20fighter%2C%20Gowdang%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Bodo%20princess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20a%20pamphlet%20containing%20the%20story%20or%20tale%20of%20the%20fictional%20or%20real%20character%20that%20the%20toy%20is%20based%20on%2C%20explains%20Kirat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sole%20purpose%20of%20these%20toys%20is%20to%20generate%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20community.%20A%20lot%20of%20research%20and%20thought%20is%20put%20into%20creating%20each%20toy.%20We%20have%20so%