ications%20before%20labour.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20fatal%20outcomes.%20Currently%2C%20all%20records%20are%20maintained%20on%20paper%2C%20and%20if%20mortality%20occurs%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20death%20remains%20unknown.%20There%20are%20no%20data-based%20analyses%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2033-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20by%20profession%2C%20Senthil%20worked%20with%20companies%20like%20Samsung%20and%20Qualcomm%20for%20seven%20years.%20But%20to%20address%20this%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20he%20started%20JioVio%20Healthcare%2C%20an%20IoT-based%20maternal%20healthcare%20startup%20that%20provides%20early%20risk%20monitoring%20services%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20developed%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20can%20predict%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F141847%2Fhigh-risk-pregnancies-get-help-with-caremother-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-risk%20pregnancies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20second%20trimester.%20This%20helps%20the%20women%20get%20early%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20if%20any%20changes%20are%20needed%20in%20nutrition%2C%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20etc.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20convert%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20into%20low-risk%20ones%20by%20ensuring%20the%20timely%20provision%20of%20medication%20and%20proper%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20mothers%20from%2014%2C328%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20Through%20a%201%2C000-day%20care%20programme%2C%20he%20has%20also%20helped%20at%20least%207%2C320%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20sister%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20lifesaving%20innovation%20for%20rural%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20came%20across%20the%20pregnancy%20healthcare%20gap%20when%20his%20sister%20was%20pregnant%20in%202016.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20career-driven%20woman%20and%20would%20miss%20her%20antenatal%20appointments%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20time.%20Also%2C%20the%20distance%20from%20her%20village%20to%20the%20hospital%20is%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Madurai%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senth