ure.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20doctor%20may%20prescribe%20different%20medications%20instead%20of%20a%20standard%20blood%20pressure%20tablet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20is%20collected%20weekly%20and%20reviewed%20by%20a%20doctor%20every%2015%20days.%20High-risk%20mothers%20are%20recommended%20to%20use%20the%20wearable%20device%20for%201%2C000%20days%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20from%20the%20fourth%20week%20of%20pregnancy%20until%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20second%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20for%20this%20service%20is%20only%20Re%201%20per%20day%2C%20covered%20by%20the%20government.%20Senthil%20says%20that%20their%20a