5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20technology%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20ends%20up%20reducing%20credit%20cost%20for%20the%20borrower.%20The%20platform%20splits%20your%20investment%20across%2010%20borrowers%20from%2010%20geographies%2C%20mitigating%20the%20risk.%20It%20has%20various%20parameters%20to%20split%20your%20capital%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20built%20an%20app%20for%20borrowers%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20an%20underwriting%20module.%20Neha%20says%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20give%20about%2015-16%20per%20cent%20return%20to%20their%2018%2C000%20investors%2C%20and%20have%20disbursed%2010%2C000%20loans.%20India%20P2P%20partners%20with%20last%20mile%20organisations%20like%20Seva%20Mandir%20and%20UNDP%20in%20pockets%20across%20the%20country.%20These%20regions%20include%20Nagaland%2C%20all%20five%20southern%20states%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20women%20everywhere%20are%20able%20to%20access%20credit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20NGOs%20and%20microfinance%20institutions%20(MFIs).%20Most%20loans%20are%20given%20to%20women%20who%20are%20part%20of%20SHGs%2C%20which%20is%20a%20powerful%20structure%20for%20accountability.%20They%20attend%20the%20weekly%20group%20meetings%20of%20SHGs%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20who%20need%20loans%20are%20given%20loans.%20Our%20loan%20officers%20visit%20the%20borrower%E2%80%99s%20place%20of%20work%20for%20due%20diligence.%20Once%20they%20are%20satisfied%2C%20the%20loans%20are%20disbursed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20loans%20disbursed%20fall%20between%20Rs%2040%2C000%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20on%20an%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIndian%20women%20have%20higher%20credit%20scores%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F